## ğŸ§ª Testing

### âœ… Backend Tests (Jest)
```bash
cd backend
npm run test
```

### âœ… Frontend Tests (React Testing Library)
```bash
cd frontend
npm test
```

### âœ… E2E Tests (Cypress)
```bash
cd frontend
npx cypress open  # or `npx cypress run`
```

**Seeding:**
```bash
cd backend
npm run seed:test
```

